<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Sri Lanka Honeymoon</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="country-hero-honey" style="background: url('/img/pexels-akalanka-98-754758-27824951.jpg');">
    <h1>Sri Lanka Honeymoon</h1>
    <p>From misty mountains to golden beaches, romance is always in the air</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Description -->
  <section class="country-description-honey">
    <p>
      Sri Lanka is a gem of the Indian Ocean, offering an unforgettable honeymoon experience. From tranquil hill-country hideaways to sun-kissed tropical beaches, couples can indulge in nature, adventure, culture, and romance — all in one island paradise.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Attractions -->
  <section class="attractions-honey">
    <h2>Most Popular Honeymoon Places in Sri Lanka</h2>
    <div class="attraction-grid-honey">

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/886e9e4109deafa857f3bd0baf9eaab3.jpg" alt="Ella">
        <h3>Ella</h3>
        <p>A charming mountain town with tea plantations, romantic train rides, and breathtaking views. Perfect for couples who love nature and peace.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/d5323b1c6be8d1a46af5ae2dfa79cd00.jpg" alt="Nuwara Eliya">
        <h3>Nuwara Eliya</h3>
        <p>Known as ‘Little England’, this cool-climate city features scenic gardens, cozy cottages, and boat rides on Gregory Lake.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/0792a814ad8c2676af437bf83d16aa7c.jpg" alt="Sigiriya Rock Fortress">
        <h3>Sigiriya</h3>
        <p>A UNESCO World Heritage Site with ancient rock gardens and stunning panoramic views. A unique and historic place to explore together.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/ea01e99af411f3a909433974fd86ff2c.jpg" alt="Mirissa Beach">
        <h3>Mirissa</h3>
        <p>A tropical beach paradise perfect for surfing, whale watching, and long romantic walks by the sunset.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/645862b546eef6cf19a65ba00f705393.jpg" alt="Kandy">
        <h3>Kandy</h3>
        <p>Sri Lanka’s cultural capital. Visit the Temple of the Tooth, enjoy a stroll by the lake, or explore the Royal Botanical Gardens together.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/c25e659464cccc0d9abb4ad51fe9973a.jpg" alt="Bentota">
        <h3>Bentota</h3>
        <p>A honeymoon favorite with palm-lined beaches, river safaris, and relaxing luxury stays by the sea.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/97635c5142ae6f4e95b2dd661ac90c14.jpg" alt="Unawatuna">
        <h3>Unawatuna</h3>
        <p>Charming coastal village with coral reefs, laid-back cafes, and some of the best snorkeling spots on the island.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/2d576fe3782155131e3b818c3c0ad83c.jpg" alt="Galle Fort">
        <h3>Galle Fort</h3>
        <p>Explore cobblestone streets, historic architecture, boutique shops, and romantic seaside dining in this Dutch colonial heritage site.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Romantic Stays in Sri Lanka -->
<section class="hotels-honey">
    <h2>Romantic Stays in Sri Lanka</h2>
    <div class="hotel-grid-honey">
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/efaed8c7b36594aeaa7b3ff29d3fd9fc.jpg" alt="Cape Weligama">
        <h3>Cape Weligama</h3>
        <p>An award-winning cliffside resort offering breathtaking ocean views, private villas, and intimate dining experiences.</p>
        <a href="https://www.resplendentceylon.com/capeweligama/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/9d07bff23ad1f188ad50b78b2d56c9c0.jpg" alt="98 Acres Resort & Spa">
        <h3>98 Acres Resort & Spa</h3>
        <p>Nestled in the hills of Ella, this eco-luxury resort is known for its romantic chalets and stunning mountain views.</p>
        <a href="https://www.resort98acres.com/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/549e7c3ddf41d1db70c720a0db062c45.jpg" alt="Heritance Kandalama">
        <h3>Heritance Kandalama</h3>
        <p>A masterpiece of eco-architecture set in the jungle with lake views, infinity pools, and candlelit dinners for two.</p>
        <a href="https://www.heritancehotels.com/kandalama/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/521337940.jpg" alt="Hilton Colombo">
        <h3>Hilton Colombo</h3>
        <p>Located in the heart of Colombo, Hilton Colombo offers panoramic views of the Indian Ocean and Beira Lake. Enjoy luxurious rooms, diverse dining options, and a serene outdoor pool — perfect for a romantic city getaway.</p>
        <a href="https://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/colhitw-hilton-colombo/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/92f8c06106b114f5aa54c501cc1bc8dc.jpg" alt="Cinnamon Bentota Beach">
        <h3>Cinnamon Bentota Beach</h3>
        <p>A beachfront resort known for golden sands, art-inspired interiors, private balconies, and water sports for adventurous couples.</p>
        <a href="https://www.cinnamonhotels.com/cinnamonbentotabeach" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/588945741.jpg" alt="Cinnamon Life – City of Dreams">
        <h3>Cinnamon Life – City of Dreams</h3>
        <p>A stunning new symbol of luxury in Colombo offering skyline views, fine dining, and modern suites — perfect for a grand honeymoon stay in the city.</p>
        <a href="https://www.cinnamonhotels.com/cinnamonlifecolombo" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>
  

</body>
</html>
